These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, handball
House: art-deco, modern
1. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
2. the modern house is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Sport   | handball | parkour |
| House     | modern    | art-deco   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, australian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, jazz
1. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
2. the australian is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Nationality   | australian | indian        |
| Music-Genre      | metal  | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, gardening
2 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit
1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Hobby   | gardening    | photography |
| Pet   | turtle | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, accountant
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike
1. the accountant is on the right of the police-officer##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Job   | police-officer      | accountant |
| Transport       | airplane | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
House: modern, futuristic
2 different games are played: snooker, go
1. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| House           | modern | futuristic |
| Game   | go    | snooker         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
