.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, lavender
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, disco
1. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Color   | lavender | grey   |
| Music-Genre         | trance | disco |

