The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, march
1. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |   2    |
| Transport   | scooter | train  |
| Birthday   | february      | march |

 